<!-- testimonial homepage -->

<div class="wrapper padded-bottom bg-grey">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="padded-mini">Discover how Shopify improved his workplace with us</h2>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <img src='<%= image_path "use-case-img.jpg" %>' alt="" class="avatar-large">
            <h3>Harley Finkelstein</h3>
            <p class="status"> Chief Operating Officer @Shopify</p>
            <p>"Ottawa's office is the flagship of Shophify, so it’s the first entrance for people who want to work with us and all our partners.
            It is important for us to break the idea that people work in standardized offices. Developpers and all our teams need a creative environment to give their best, and the possibility of changing our decoration every 3 months is an amazing way of doing so. It is a good opportunity for people from outside to understand and discover why our teams are so proud of their office and connect with our culture. Art helps break down barriers and is now a new possible way to create social link. I like the idea of renting art from unknown talented artists and change my workplace in a real living art gallery. We just pick a new artist every 3 months and Seeedr takes care of the rest !"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
          <div class="testimonial-content iframe-container text-center">
            <div>
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j0dH_V34GSM?ecver=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

